					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>I don't know if there ever actually was an intention to actually pick one of the proposals and drop the others</p> </blockquote> <p>In real life, no. In-universe, depends on your headcanon.</p> <blockquote> <p>SO we should probably stop calling them proposals.</p> </blockquote> <p>For a lot of readers, part of the enjoyment of this format is the &quot;proposal&quot; setup. I personally am not certain this is a change most of the community would be insistent on?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
